Usage: fixBondPad [-help] {{-ioInstName <InstName> [-pinName <pinName>]} | -selected }

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-ioInstName <InstName>     # specifies the name of I/O instance
                           # (string, required)
-pinName <pinName>         # specifies the name of the pin inside the instance
                           # (string, optional)
-selected                  # assigns a fixed status to a selected bond pad
                           # (bool, required)